        %li One of the Big Five
        %li Small brain for an animal this size
        %li Has exceptionally thick skin 1-1.5cm, almost like armored plating.
        %li Has a pointed mouth for eating leaves form trees and bushes
        %li Enemies: Few, except lion, hyena and other large predators when young
        %li Longevity:
